data.text:
Eyewitness

A fast-paced thriller seen through the eyes of two teenagers. A clandestine meeting between school friends Philip and Henning unravels into a spiral of murder, corruption and gang warfare. Meeting one night in secret at a remote sand quarry, the young men find themselves attracted to each other, but their illicit encounter is dramatically interrupted by the arrival of a car containing four men.
